Name: :ref:`periodicReport <periodicReport>`
Description: Periodic **report** generated at time interval or time of day.

Name: :ref:`paramAlertON <paramAlertON>`
Description: Immediate **alert** generated by high/low threshold trigger.

Name: :ref:`paramAlertOFF <paramAlertOFF>`
Description: Immediate **alert** generated by return to normal from outside threshold.

Name: :ref:`paramAlertChange <paramAlertChange>`
Description: Immediate **alert** generated by change threshold trigger.

Name: :ref:`error <error>`
Description: Error alert due to Modbus/serial or configuration problem.
